This family curates historical VRPTW benchmark material originating from
Solomon (1987), Gehring and Homberger (1999), and the SINTEF VRPTW benchmark
convention. This license notice does not claim to relicense third-party
benchmark definitions or third-party best-known solution sources beyond the
rights held by MAMUT-routing contributors.
